{"tid":1586004,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家冷靜啲，「私了」真係有問題","createTime":"2019-09-21T18:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T20:36:06.000Z","uid":64981,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"958bfc63bdb5427eab5cecd8f73c70dfa0a248ca","tid":1586004,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:32:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武手足唔係「私了」<br />\n係「以武制暴」<br />\n係「保護記者」<br />\n係「打擊黑社會」<br />\n係「打擊惡勢力」</span><br />\n<br />\n對外唔好講「私了」，好撚大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFb文宣：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2991280674277871?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2787894407949833%2Fposts%2F2991280674277871%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=1ce49398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2991280674277871?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HqiDSrQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqiDSrQ.jpg&h=86ace1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#警黑勾結 #請廣傳】<br />\n相關報道：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2m6bbvG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2m6bbvG&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=94f38b43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2m6bbvG</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2mliEam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mliEam&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=3de74537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2mliEam</a><br />\n<br />\n9月21日 元朗 黑夜<br />\n<br />\n有大批親中黑社會，在元朗空群而出，向女性示威者，或女記者、女救護埋手非禮，甚至襲擊她們。其間，有示威者上前，以武力將他們制服。遇襲反擊的女示威者大叫：「咪以為我哋好蝦呀！」<br />\n<br />\n=============================<br />\n【延伸閱讀：7.21元朗警黑勾結事件簿】<br />\n持棍白衫撐警份子，手持武器下警察放人：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2kU9FMX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kU9FMX&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=2d7c34e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2kU9FMX</a><br />\n<br />\n市民路過元朗，被白衫撐警份子圍毆：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2mjID1T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mjID1T&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=b41ef5ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2mjID1T</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗街坊求助，報案室嘲「怕危險唔好出街」：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lZaIeP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lZaIeP&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=4a343c81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lZaIeP</a><br />\n<br />\n平民比警察更快到場支援，被撐警份子打至頭破血流：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2kS92Ug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kS92Ug&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=1ab5f271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2kS92Ug</a><br />\n<br />\n鄉紳黑社會承認恐襲責任，警察沒有拘捕：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2kumz4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kumz4k&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=c277d5f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2kumz4k</a><br />\n=============================<br />\n#警察 #警黑勾結 #黑警 #黑社會 #元朗"},{"pid":"2805ad0fea053cefbae22c8011e959e8792976a0","tid":1586004,"uid":76776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:33:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef7e0a7660bee10b18a7452dcb2e802ff65b0982","tid":1586004,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:33:45.000Z","msg":"自衛圍毆"},{"pid":"64c6862eded07b1927a02aa5b1fa06831f826cff","tid":1586004,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50e2613778f09f747c98489fa895334534a76bc7","tid":1586004,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:36:06.000Z","msg":"保護香港市民既前線,<br />\n<br />\n我代表香港市民感謝您們的付出,<br />\n為了阻止元朗黑幫, 以及來自內地的愛國流氓的無差別攻擊市民,<br />\n在對方動手之際, 當機立斷,<br />\n雖然香港警察包庇並釋放這些滋事份子,<br />\n但是您們放棄自己的安全, 身段和左膠們的眼光,<br />\n俠義相教, 阻止了這些滋事份子的惡行和中共的企圖<br />\n這高尚的情操和表現, 是我們香港人的光榮<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線門 加油!<br />\n香港人 加油!</span></span></strong>"}]}